  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf \u0b89\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Notice of Petrol Station Owners Association",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Fuel will be distributed from next Thursday (21) based on the National Fuel Permit, Kumara Rajapaksa, President of the Petrol Station Owners Association, said yesterday (18).",
        "He also pointed out that there is no point in standing in queues in front of CPC petrol stations.",
        "From Thursday, fuel will be dispensed only on the basis of QR code and the last digit of the vehicle number plate, he said and asked the people who were currently queuing to leave the queues.",
        "He added that only vehicle owners with the last digit of the vehicle number plate, which are 0, 1 and 2, will be able to get fuel on the 21st.",
        "It is noteworthy that Monday and Thursday are reserved for the digits 0, 1, 2, Tuesday and Friday for the final digits 3, 4, 5 and Wednesday, Saturday and Sunday for the final digits 6, 7, 8, 9."
      ],
